question: Within a radius of 40 kilometers, what café can I find located in the southeast of Canopy by Hilton Washington DC Bethesda North, North Bethesda, MD?
sql:
WITH origin AS  (SELECT ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-77.116876 39.050782)',4326)::geography AS geometry)
SELECT * FROM pois, origin
WHERE ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-77.116876 39.050782)',4326)::geography, 40000)
AND amenity = 'cafe'
AND degrees(ST_Azimuth(origin.geometry, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN 112.5 AND 157.5;

answers.poi_name: Roots and Blooms Flower Shop & Cafe

answers.description: Coffee shop with ice cream, baked goods, sandwiches, gifts and other deli products.
